Immediately install Extension Manager from the GNOME Software app

Install the Extensions: 
- Blur My Shell
- Fly-Pie
- Vitals
- Espresso
- GSConnect
- Just Perfection
- Vertical Workspaces
- Hanabi

Enable: 
- Applications Menu
- User Themes
- Workspace Indicator

File Manager/Programs to download:
Nemo file manager

Usual Theme:
Icons: Retropixel
Shell: Rosepine
Legacy Applications: BellePintosGrande

Fonts:
Interface Text: RM2000Alt Medium 18
Documeht Text: Cantarell Regular 11
Monospace text: Source Code Pro Regular 10
Legacy Window Titles: RM2000Alt Medium 18

Link to RM2000Alt font:
https://www.deviantart.com/tabmok99/art/RPG-Maker-2000-Font-Pack-900800437

